cs.DB, cs.PL, cs.SE, cs.LG, cs.DC 

This paper is about building a database query engine using a high-level programming language, which falls under the category of database systems (cs.DB). The paper also discusses the use of generative programming, which is a technique used in programming languages (cs.PL) and the importance of abstraction and decoupling in software development (cs.SE). The paper also evaluates the performance of the query engine, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC).
